checkVictoryConditionsAndReturnTimeUntilRoundEnd() - Method in class aoop.asteroids.model.game.ServerGame
In this function, all victory conditions are checked.
If they are triggered, corresponding messages are added to this game.
Afterwards, the time until the game is over is returned as a number.

Victory Conditions:
Singleplayer: All asteroids are destroyed.
Client - Class in aoop.asteroids.udp
 
Client(String, int, boolean, String) - Constructor for class aoop.asteroids.udp.Client
This constructor creates a new ClientSender with the specified host and port, as well as starting a ClientReceiver thread that listens for packets on the same socket.
After this, a ClientGame is started; this is the graphical representation of the game on the client-side.
